</p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-dISoPS kgxkyr pf-56_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-57_ pf-text-1"><strong>Regular training </strong>- Ensure that employees undergo regular first aid training, including hands-on practice on techniques such as CPR and AED usage.






















